!INTRODUCTION
!
!INTERSIL WISHES TO THANK YOU FOR YOUR INTEREST IN OUR HFA3XXX
!TRANSISTOR ARRAY PRODUCTS. 
!THIS FILE CONTAINS S-PARAMETER DATA AND PACKAGE MODELS AND IS PROVIDED FOR 
!YOUR CONVENIENCE TO HELP IN EVALUATING INTERSIL'S NEW UHF1 TRANSISTORS.
!NOTE THAT THIS DATA REPRESENTS TYPICAL VALUES AND IS NOT TO BE UNDERSTOOD
!AS GUARANTEED PARAMETERS.
!
!THE DATA IS PROVIDED IN TWO PARTS IN THIS FILE.  THE FIRST PART OF 
!THIS FILE CONTAINS S PARAMETERS DERIVED FROM EVALUATION OF THE PRODUCT IN 
!UNPACKAGED (DIE) FORM. NOTE THAT DIE S-PARAMETER DATA IS PROVIDED OVER A 
!RANGE OF FREQUENCIES, VOLTAGES AND COLLECTOR CURRENT CONDITIONS. THE 
!S-PARAMETER FILES ARE FORMATTED TO BE COMPATIBLE WITH SUPERCOMPACT AND 
!TOUCHSTONE RF SIMULATORS.
!THE SECOND HALF OF THE FILE PROVIDES PACKAGE CHARACTERISTICS INCLUDING 
!INDUCTANCE AND CAPACITANCE COMPONENTS FOR EACH PIN OF THE 14 AND 16 PIN SOIC 
!PACKAGES.  TOGETHER THIS DATA SHOULD PROVIDE YOU THE NECESSARY INFORMATION 
!TO SIMULATE THE PERFORMANCE OF EACH PARTICULAR TRANSISTOR IN THE HFA3XXX 
!FAMILY.  
!
