------------------
EQUIVALANT CIRCUIT
------------------


	PCB GND PLANE   o_______
				|
				|
			       [Cb] 
				|
				|
	PCB INTERFACE,  o_______o________[Le]________o
	I/O #1                                       |
						     |
						    [Cm]
						     |
						     |
	PCB INTERFACE,  o_______o________[Le]________o
	I/O #2                  |
				|
			       [Cb]
				|
				|
	PCB GND PLANE   o_______|



	where
	Cb: Effective capacitance between the end of the pin and PCB ground
	Le: Effective self-inductance of individual pin
	Cm: Mutual capacitance between the adjascent pins


